1 (b) An action for adverse possession shall not be maintained unless the
2 plaintiff has provided the record owner of the property with notice of the
3 plaintiff’s claim to the property not less than six months prior to the expiration
4 of the 15-year period established by subsection (a) of this section.
5 Sec. 2. EFFECTIVE DATE
6 This act shall take effect on passage.
